content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4820.46 - Use of limited period bingo cards

State Regulations

Each card shall be used for one game only and be
indelibly marked by the player while in use in such manner as to render such
card void and unusable thereafter. Limited period bingo cards shall not be used
in the conduct of any other type of bingo games. Notes
